<div class="alert alert-info">
	<h2 class="h3">Notice - Removal of MathJax</h2>
	<p>Since MathML is now supported natively by browsers, all instances of MathJax have been removed from WET-BOEW.</p>
</div>

<section>
	<h2>Purpose</h2>
	<p>MathML enabled the display of mathematical formulas. Because some browsers did not support this functionality natively, this polyfill emulated the same functionality using MathJax.</p>
</section>

